name: Warm Meal
description: A hot pot full of fresh ingredients.  The tiny number of spores promotes a moderately spicy taste that keeps your body warm.  Stores 120,000 HP and 8,000 SP. Restores 500 HP every 6s when HP is below 70% and 50 SP every 6s when SP is below 40%

name: Warm Stone
description: Use to become immune to Freeze for 1 min. Cannot work with [Whisper Stone] [Sleepless Stone] and [Activity Stone].

name: Water Axe [1]
description: The axe with the power of water. Using the latest craftsmanship, Crystal Blue is combined with the Rune array to make the axe.

name: Water Axe [2]
description: The axe with the power of water. Using the latest craftsmanship, Crystal Blue is combined with the Rune array to make the axe.

name: Water Blessing Box
description: Use it and get the Magic Dominator Quietness (male) or Lilith Ocean Blue (female) beauty contact lens from the Beauty of Eyes in Prontera.

name: Water Egg
description: The egg with water attribute. After use, Your attack turns into water attribute and the effect lasts 30 minutes. Unable to coexist with Mystic Frozen.

name: Water from Fountain of Youth
description: Drink the water from the legendary Fountain of Youth to be young forever!

name: Water Knife [1]
description: Dagger with the power of water. Using the latest craftsmanship, Crystal Blue is combined with the Rune array to make the sword.

name: Water Knife [2]
description: Dagger with the power of water. Using the latest craftsmanship, Crystal Blue is combined with the Rune array to make the sword.

name: Water of Forgetting
description: The great product of Midgard's top magic. Adventurers with Water of Forgetting can visit Mayfair Linse to forget all skills that have been learned, and all skill points and Zeny will be returned.

name: Water Sword [2]
description: A knife with a blue blade and the power of water.

name: Water Sword [3]
description: A knife with a blue blade and the power of water.

name: Wave Witch Hat
description: Popular among young demons for its noble smell, the saying goes, "if you wear it, the obeaune will stop singing with shame."

name: Weapon Repair Alloy
description: A precious metal made by Blacksmith. Use it and all your damaged items and weapons will be repaired. They will also be protected for 1 second.

name: Wedding Veil
description: Bridal veil only for girls at wedding.

name: Wedding Veil Blueprint
description: Bridal veil only for girls at wedding.
